<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>射手座 on Lucky Stone</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/tags/%E5%B0%84%E6%89%8B%E5%BA%A7/</link><description>Recent content in 射手座 on Lucky Stone</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://luckystonetw.com/tags/%E5%B0%84%E6%89%8B%E5%BA%A7/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>火象星座能量解析：牡羊獅子射手的火焰性格與守護水晶</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%81%AB%E8%B1%A1%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E7%89%A1%E7%BE%8A%E7%8D%85%E5%AD%90%E5%B0%84%E6%89%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%81%AB%E7%84%B0%E6%80%A7%E6%A0%BC%E8%88%87%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%81%AB%E8%B1%A1%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E7%89%A1%E7%BE%8A%E7%8D%85%E5%AD%90%E5%B0%84%E6%89%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%81%AB%E7%84%B0%E6%80%A7%E6%A0%BC%E8%88%87%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;火焰有很多種燃燒的方式——有的像剛擦亮的火柴，瞬間點燃整片黑暗；有的像壁爐裡的炭火，持續散發溫暖的光芒；有的像營火的火星，隨風飄散到意想不到的遠方。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>紫水晶星座配對：雙魚、水瓶、射手為什麼特別有緣？</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E9%85%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%9B%99%E9%AD%9A%E6%B0%B4%E7%93%B6%E5%B0%84%E6%89%8B%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%A3/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E9%85%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%9B%99%E9%AD%9A%E6%B0%B4%E7%93%B6%E5%B0%84%E6%89%8B%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%A3/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;同樣一顆紫水晶，有人戴了感覺渾身舒暢，有人帶了幾個月幾乎沒感覺。這不全然是「信不信的問題」——星座跟水晶的共振確實有差。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>